name: Google calendar embedding practice
tagline: My practice of Google calendar embedding in website.
body:
How to embed Google calendar in html page
<iframe src="https://www.google.com/calendar/embed?src=s8klli5ruuqg12cqj4i1q64rlk%40group.calendar.google.com&ctz=Asia/Calcutta" style="border: 0" width="800" height="600" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
